title: [Western Waterway, Broken Harbor]
description: Moonlight calls attention to the glistening cliffs towering above the ocean as a formidable barrier in the east.  Shadows dance across a small reef established from fan corals and branching corals near the shoreline, and dark liquid washes over the living structure in foamy waves as it laps against the island.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, southwest, west
